name: Simple Series Vol. 2: The Number Puzzle neo
overview: The game is to put a number from 1 to 9 in the square. However, the numbers are numbers not in the vertical row / horizontal row of the square, even if there are the same numbers in the block mass for each vertical 3 horizontal and horizontal 3 square NG. In addition to this normal game mode "standard", 3 × 3 block mass is rotated to combine "trick mode" installed! A new dimension number puzzle hits your brain! There are 4 levels of difficulty, and beginners and super advanced users can enjoy it altogether!
